<p id="yui_3_17_2_6_1450029850386_3657">Here are the birthdays:<br>10th - DOOM<br>14th - Commander Keen 1-3<br>15th - Commander Keen 4-5<br>23rd - Hyperspace Delivery Boy &amp; Heretic (two 'H' games on the same day!)</p><p id="yui_3_17_2_6_1450029850386_3658">In case you were wondering about the screenshot, it was referencing a future Keen game we planned on making: Keen 7 - The Universe is Toast! But we started working immediately on Wolfenstein 3D and........the rest is history.</p>]]></description></item><item><title>Short Interview</title><category>press</category><dc:creator>John Romero</dc:creator><pubDate>Tue, 18 Nov 2008 18:16:00 +0000</pubDate><link>https://rome.ro/news/2015/12/13/short-interview</link><guid isPermaLink="false">566d855a841abafcc8ed19c4:566d86c02399a3bdabbc9bdf:566db5a5df40f3a73185f668</guid><description><![CDATA[<figure class="
