<p>Unknown to me and maybe even id Software way back when, 12 years ago a couple Hungarian DOOM novels were written and released (bottom two books). Of course I know all about the English DOOM novels by Daffyd ab Hugh but these are a surprise to me.</p><p>Scans of these books are posted in my DOOM photo section.</p><p>The top two books comprise Masters of DOOM split up. The translation of the text is "DooM Legendája (Legend of DooM). Hogyan változtatta meg John Carmack és John Romero a világot (How did John Carmack and John Romero change the world)".</p><p>Thanks for the info, Timea Cseke (IMPgirl)!</p>]]></description></item><item><title>OGDC Interview</title><dc:creator>John Romero</dc:creator><pubDate>Tue, 15 May 2007 18:39:00 +0000</pubDate><link>https://rome.ro/news/2015/12/16/ogdc-interview</link><guid isPermaLink="false">566d855a841abafcc8ed19c4:566d86c02399a3bdabbc9bdf:5671bdb540667a634d0caad9</guid><description><![CDATA[<figure class="
